  "prompt": "Which are the best news website in India?",
  "response": "As of 2023, several news websites in India are widely regarded for their credibility, comprehensive coverage, and user engagement. Here are some of the best news websites in India:\n\n1. **The Times of India (TOI)** - One of the largest and most popular English-language newspapers and websites in India, offering a wide range of news on various topics.\n\n2. **NDTV** - Known for its reliable news coverage, NDTV provides articles and videos on Indian and international news, politics, entertainment, and more.\n\n3. **The Indian Express** - Offers detailed reporting and analysis, and is highly respected for its investigative journalism and editorial integrity.\n\n4. **Hindustan Times** - Another major English-language newspaper with a robust online presence, covering national and international news, business, sports, and entertainment.\n\n5. **The Hindu** - Known for its thorough and unbiased news reporting, The Hindu focuses on national and international news with in-depth analysis.\n\n6. **News18** - Offers comprehensive coverage of news from India and around the world, including live updates, detailed articles, and multimedia content.\n\n7. **Scroll.in** - Provides insightful analysis, news and in-depth reporting on various socio-political issues, culture, and environment.\n\n8. **India Today** - A well-known news outlet that covers a wide range of topics including politics, sports, entertainment, and lifestyle, with regular updates and multimedia content.\n\n9. **BBC India** - Part of the BBC World Service, this site offers credible and detailed reporting on India-specific news alongside global coverage.\n\n10. **The Wire** - An independent news website known for its investigative journalism and in-depth political analysis.\n\nThese platforms are popular among readers for their comprehensive and reliable news coverage. It is always advisable to cross-check news from multiple sources to get a balanced perspective.",
